00100 void CDFDataTest::FileHeaderTest()
00101 {
00102         // Put something into the header.
00103         data->SetArrayCols(45);
00104 
00105         // Get the header.
00106         FileHeader* fh = data->GetFileHeader();
00107         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fh);
00108 
00109         // Try to read the thing from the header.
00110         ParameterNameValueType pvt;
00111         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(fh->GetGenericDataHdr()->FindNameValParam(CDF_COLS_PARAM, pvt));
00112         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(pvt.GetValueUInt32() == 45);
00113 }
